		<ExpectedPoint>95</ExpectedPoint>
		<TextToType>Through three cheese trees three free fleas flew. While these fleas flew, freezy breeze blew. Freezy breeze made these three trees freeze. Freezy trees made these trees' cheese freeze. That's what made these three free fleas sneeze.</TextToType>
